"title": "7346: death penalty",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7346: death penalty",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The lawful taking of human life by the civil or military authorities. The death penalty was inflicted by all nations in the ancient world. In Israel, the main method was stoning, amongst other nations, other forms such as hanging, beheading and crucifixion were used.</p>\n<h2>The ultimate authority for the death penalty lies with God alone</h2>\n<h3>Examples of God taking human life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:29\">EXO 12:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:35\">NUM 16:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam6:19\">1SA 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:38\">1SA 25:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:7\">2SA 6:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr13:10\">1CH 13:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:23\">ACT 12:23</a></p>\n<h3>God may delegate his authority to human beings</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:6\">GEN 9:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:15\">JOS 7:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:25\">JOS 7:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:3\">1SA 15:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:32-1Sam15:33\">1SA 15:32–15:33</a></p>\n<h3>The role of the civil authority</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts25:11\">ACT 25:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:1\">ROM 13:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:3-Rom13:4\">ROM 13:3–13:4</a></p>\n<h2>Causes of the death penalty</h2>\n<h3>Sacrilege</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:12-Exod19:13\">EXO 19:12–19:13</a></p>\n<h3>Serious abuse of one's parents</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:15\">EXO 21:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:17\">EXO 21:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:18-Deut21:21\">DEU 21:18–21:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:4\">MAT 15:4</a></p>\n<h3>Adultery</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:10\">LEV 20:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:22\">DEU 22:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:5\">JHN 8:5</a></p>\n<h3>Blasphemy</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:16\">LEV 24:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:7\">JHN 19:7</a></p>\n<h3>Idolatry</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:2\">LEV 20:2</a></p>\n<h3>Immorality</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:11-Lev20:16\">LEV 20:11–20:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:21-Deut22:25\">DEU 22:21–22:25</a></p>\n<h3>Kidnapping</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:16\">EXO 21:16</a></p>\n<h3>Murder</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:6\">GEN 9:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:12\">EXO 21:12</a></p>\n<h3>Rebellion</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:12\">DEU 17:12</a></p>\n<h3>Sabbath-breaking</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:14-Exod31:15\">EXO 31:14–31:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:32-Num15:36\">NUM 15:32–15:36</a></p>\n<h3>Witchcraft</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:27\">LEV 20:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:9\">1SA 28:9</a></p>\n<h3>Rape of a betrothed virgin</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:23-Deut22:29\">DEU 22:23–22:29</a></p>\n<h3>Bestiality</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:19\">EXO 22:19</a></p>\n<h3>Child sacrifice</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:2-Lev20:5\">LEV 20:2–20:5</a></p>\n<h2>Means of executing the death penalty</h2>\n<h3>Beheading</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:19\">GEN 40:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:27\">MRK 6:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:9-Matt14:10\">MAT 14:9–14:10</a></p>\n<h3>Burning</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:6\">DAN 3:6</a></p>\n<h3>Crucifixion</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:26\">MAT 27:26</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:15\">MRK 15:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:16\">JHN 19:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:38\">MAT 27:38</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:27\">MRK 15:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:33\">LUK 23:33</a></p>\n<h3>Hanging</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:22\">GEN 40:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:22-Deut21:23\">DEU 21:22–21:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:30\">ACT 5:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:13\">GAL 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>Impalement</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:11\">EZR 6:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:23\">EST 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth5:14\">EST 5:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth7:9-Esth7:10\">EST 7:9–7:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:12-Esth9:13\">EST 9:12–9:13</a></p>\n<h3>Stoning</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:23\">LEV 24:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:18-Deut21:21\">DEU 21:18–21:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:2\">LEV 20:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:14\">LEV 24:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:35\">NUM 15:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:23\">LEV 24:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:36\">NUM 15:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:25\">JOS 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:11-1Kgs21:13\">1KI 21:11–21:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:21\">2CH 24:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:54-Acts7:59\">ACT 7:54–7:59</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:58-John8:59\">JHN 8:58–8:59</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:31-John10:33\">JHN 10:31–10:33</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:3-John8:11\">JHN 8:3–8:11</a> <em>Jesus Christ refuses to carry out a stoning.</em></p>\n<h3>The sword</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:27\">EXO 32:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:33\">1SA 15:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:18-1Sam22:19\">1SA 22:18–22:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:29\">1KI 2:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:46\">1KI 2:46</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr23:14-2Chr23:15\">2CH 23:14–23:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:5\">DAN 2:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:2\">ACT 12:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:37\">HEB 11:37</a></p>\n<h3>Wild beasts</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:16\">DAN 6:16</a></p>\n<h2>The commutation of the death penalty</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:15\">GEN 4:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:13\">EXO 21:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:29-Exod21:30\">EXO 21:29–21:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:6\">NUM 35:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:42\">DEU 4:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:1-Deut19:10\">DEU 19:1–19:10</a></p>",
